Kamala Harris, the radical Senator from California with a socialist agenda, just announced an upcoming visit to our own Greensboro, NC. Her priorities are strikingly different from mine:

Kamala Harris supports socialism, gun confiscation, free healthcare for illegal immigrants, abortions for all, and Hollywood values like the Green New Deal. 

Meanwhile, I’m fighting for economic freedom, a strong border wall, tax cuts and spending cuts, the right to life, and for good North Carolina common sense. I will never waver in my fight.

She’s coming here because the path for Democrats to the White House runs right through North Carolina, and right through our district.

That’s why I’m assembling a team of our top conservative supporters, whom I can count on to tell Kamala Harris that we will keep North Carolina "Trump Country" in 2020.

Will you join me today in telling Kamala Harris to keep her socialist agenda out of NC?
http://petitions.tedbudd.com/kamalaharris
